OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUkraine war: People can    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwelcome refugees into own  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhomes - PM                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Boris Johnson has defended the UK's    
OL,6, response to the refugee crisis and said
OL,7, an upcoming scheme will allow Britons  
OL,8, to take Ukrainians into their homes.   
OL,10,FHe told Sky News the UK would be       
OL,11,F"generous" to those fleeing Ukraine,   
OL,12,Fand that details of a second visa      
OL,13,Fscheme would be announced on Monday.   
OL,15,FDefending the current visa rules, the  
OL,16,FPM said: "People want us to be generous
OL,17,Fbut also careful."                     
OL,19,FThe UK has been criticised for taking  
OL,20,Fin just about 1,000 refugees so far.   
